      "para_id": "Q005011.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Ibbi-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Ur-aba , the scribe , child of Adda-kala , the overseer of the animal-fatteners , is your servant ."
    }
  ],
